    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game synopsis:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious program called “Cupid’s Chatroom” suddenly appears on your PC, transporting you into a private chatroom. You find yourself joined by five others, who have also been dragged into the server—and it turns out they’re your potential bachelors?! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the bachelors</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157200/extras/b762a46656a5ed5d1f60e9fbf732cfd9.avif?t=1746288404\" width=800 height=935 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157200/extras/12faf45a10565e7e4047ff81a1b0ff59.avif?t=1746288404\" width=800 height=935 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157200/extras/50ad290bc631958a7d5a4d48fc6576db.avif?t=1746288404\" width=800 height=935 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157200/extras/0206b5bda904cb49cf7df55e4a1e1f64.avif?t=1746288404\" width=800 height=935 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157200/extras/b1966f07a14f180f54f89215116d4ad5.avif?t=1746288404\" width=800 height=935 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Content warning:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cupid's Chatroom is an 18+ dating chatsim. The full game contains NSFW content that is only intended for players 18 years and older. The demo is SFW.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other warnings:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mentions of violence </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Topics on trauma, depression, and other mental illnesses </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strong language, cursing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 love interests to get to know until Day 3.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~20k words for each route.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pronoun options and customizable username. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Video and voice calls. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Receive selfies from the LIs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partial voice acting.  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of banter. Like a lot.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thank you!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for playing the demo of Cupid's Chatroom. We're planning to launch a Kickstarter to help fund the full development of the game. Follow the studio on Tumblr, Twitter, and Bluesky for updates on the game's development ♡</p>",
